display_title = "The Vault"
text = "A terrible force twists you around and brings you to your knees. Pain stabs through your legs. With enormous effort, you look up into the face of Sister Schaefer.

How did she get down here so quickly? How is she holding you down? [i]Where did she get that knife?[/i]

She walks forwards— careful to not disturb any of the objects around her — until she's directly over you. She stares at you for a while, considering. And then she lifts her knife, huge and curved like the moon, over your head.
"
